
One Lake & Lakehouses
======================
One lake ios basically like a managed data lake that is storing all our data. It is just an invisible layer taht is just acting as this managhed data lake.
It is not only storing all of the data within our account, but it is also creating or we are also able to create so-called shortcuts to external files. ( so without moving the data, without creating complex data pipelines, the data through those shortcuts appeares to be in out one lake)

LakeHouse - They are like a mixture of data lakes, which is more flexible, and then also the more performance oriented and more analytical solution of data warehouses.
Lakehouse is an item created within our workspace.
